getOrCreateSharedProvider

public static Provider getOrCreateSharedProvider(Context context,
                                                 ProviderOptions options)
Returns the previously set shared provider reference. If there is no such reference, then it will create a new provider using the given context and options, set it as the new shared provider and return it.

Parameters:
context - The context of the currently running application.
options - The options for the provider to be returned, including credentials and provider identifications
Returns:
A instance of the payment provider ready to be used
Since:
2.0.0
